hoc2015_reinfFeedbackMsg: E āhei ana te pātene "{backButton}" te pēhi kia hoki anō ki te tākaro i tō kēmu.
hoc2015_move_right_instructions: "Kei te hiahiatia tērā mara konganuku [scrapmetal1]. Māu e tiki, BB-8?"
hoc2015_move_right_down_instructions: "Kei te hiahiatia ētahi mara konganuku [scrapmetal2] anō. Ka riro i a koe ngā konganuku katoa i tēnei rohe?"
hoc2015_move_finale_instructions: "Kia 4 anō ngā mara konganuku [scrapmetal2]. Ka kitea e koe?"
hoc2015_event_two_items_instructions: "R2-D2, māu tētahi karere arohaehae e tuku ki ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot]."
hoc2015_event_two_items_instructions2: Whakanekehia a R2-D2 mā te whakamahi i ngā pātuhi pere.
hoc2015_event_four_items_instructions: "Kia tere te haere atu i ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot] katoa."
hoc2015_score_instructions: "Me tae atu ki ngā Rebel Pilots!"
hoc2015_score_instructions2: Me tāpiri piro. Tāpiritia ngā piro ina riro ia Rebel Pilot [rebelpilot] i a R2-D2. Me riro i te 900 ngā piro kia toa.
hoc2015_win_lose_instructions2: Tāpiritia kia 100 ngā piro ina riro i a R2-D2 tētahi Rebel Pilot [rebelpilot]. Tangohia kia 100 ina riro i a ia tētahi Stormtrooper [stormtrooper]. Me riro i te 200 ngā piro hei hipa i te panga. (Whakamahia te Mynock [mynock] kia māmā ake te mahi.)
hoc2015_add_characters_instructions: "Ki taku titiro, kei te nui haere ngā mahi i tēnei aorangi."
hoc2015_add_characters_instructions2: Tāpirihia kia toru ngā Poaka Puffer [pufferpig] ki te aorangi. Kātahi, ka haere ki te tiki.
hoc2015_chain_characters_instructions2: Ka riro i a koe tētahi Tauntaun [tauntaun], whakaputaina kia rua, neke atu rānei ngā Mynocks [mynock]. Me riro i te 8 ngā Mynocks.
hoc2015_multiply_characters_instructions: Ka whakaputaina e koe ngā Mouse Droids [mousedroid] e rua, neke atu rānei hei ngā wā ka riro i a R2-D2 tētahi Droid? Me riro i te 20 ngā Mouse Droids.
hoc2015_change_setting_instructions: "Kua eke ki te wā kia toro aorangi anō."
hoc2015_change_setting_instructions2: Whakamahia ngā tono hou hei panoni i tō karetao me tōna tere. Kātahi, me riro i ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot].
hoc2015_event_free_instructions2: Kua mau i a koe ngā pūkenga katoa ināianei hei waihanga i tō ake panga. Tēnā, tūhuratia, rāwekehia ngā momo Tono me ngā Takunetanga rerekē katoa. Kia muti i a koe, pēhia te pātene Mutu kia haere tonu.
